Interface Node

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BoundMethodReferenceNode, CastNode, ClassNode, ConstNode, ConstructorInvokeNode, EmptyArrayNode, LambdaNode, LambdaNode.Param, LiteralArrayNode, LiteralNode, MethodInvokeNode, MethodReferenceNode, TypeInferringNode, UnboundMethodReferenceNode, VarNode
